{
    "title": "FTCFormer: Fuzzy Token Clustering Transformer for Image Classification",
    "authors": [
        "Muyi Bao",
        "Changyu Zeng",
        "Yifan Wang",
        "Zhengni Yang",
        "Zimu Wang",
        "Guangliang Cheng",
        "Jun Qi",
        "Wei Wang"
    ],
    "abstract": "Transformer-based deep neural networks have achieved remarkable success across various computer vision tasks, largely attributed to their long-range self-attention mechanism and scalability. However, most transformer architectures embed images into uniform, grid-based vision tokens, neglecting the underlying semantic meanings of image regions, resulting in suboptimal feature representations. To address this issue, we propose Fuzzy Token Clustering Transformer (FTCFormer), which incorporates a novel clustering-based downsampling module to dynamically generate vision tokens based on the semantic meanings instead of spatial positions. It allocates fewer tokens to less informative regions and more to represent semantically important regions, regardless of their spatial adjacency or shape irregularity. To further enhance feature extraction and representation, we propose a Density Peak Clustering-Fuzzy K-Nearest Neighbor (DPC-FKNN) mechanism for clustering center determination, a Spatial Connectivity Score (SCS) for token assignment, and a channel-wise merging (Cmerge) strategy for token merging. Extensive experiments on 32 datasets across diverse domains validate the effectiveness of FTCFormer on image classification, showing consistent improvements over the TCFormer baseline, achieving gains of improving 1.43% on five fine-grained datasets, 1.09% on six natural image datasets, 0.97% on three medical datasets and 0.55% on four remote sensing datasets.",
    "summary": "本文提出了一种基于模糊令牌聚类的视觉Transformer（FTCFormer），用于图像分类任务。针对传统Transformer将图像均匀切分为网格化令牌、忽略语义区域差异的问题，FTCFormer引入聚类下采样模块，根据语义重要性动态生成令牌：对重要区域分配更多令牌，对不重要区域分配更少令牌。具体创新包括：DPC-FKNN用于聚类中心确定（融合KNN和模糊KNN集，增强对不均匀数据和噪声的鲁棒性）、空间连通性分数（SCS）用于令牌分配（结合共享近邻和局部密度，缓解高维空间距离失效问题）、以及通道级合并策略（Cmerge）用于令牌融合（保留通道间语义差异）。在32个跨域数据集上的实验表明，FTCFormer在细粒度、自然图像、医学图像和遥感数据集上分别比基线TCFormer提升1.43%、1.09%、0.97%和0.55%。",
    "keywords": [
        "Vision Transformer",
        "Token Clustering",
        "Fuzzy K-Nearest Neighbor",
        "Density Peak Clustering",
        "Dynamic Token Generation",
        "Image Classification",
        "Semantic Tokenization",
        "Channel-wise Merging"
    ],
    "contributions": [
        "提出了FTCFormer架构，通过基于语义的聚类下采样模块动态分配视觉令牌，增强重要区域的特征表示。",
        "设计了模糊令牌聚类与合并（FTCM）模块，集成DPC-FKNN聚类中心确定、SCS令牌分配和Cmerge通道级令牌合并三个关键组件。",
        "在32个跨域数据集上进行了全面实验，FTCFormer在细粒度、自然图像、医学和遥感数据集上分别比TCFormer提升1.43%、1.09%、0.97%和0.55%，验证了其鲁棒性和泛化能力。"
    ],
    "limitations": [
        "在简单、低分辨率数据集（如MNIST、CIFAR类）上提升有限，仅分别提高0.21%和0.06%，表明方法在近饱和场景中收益较小。",
        "聚类和合并过程引入额外计算开销，可能不适用于对推理速度要求极高的实时应用场景。",
        "DPC-FKNN和SCS中涉及的K值（如K_Fuzzy、K_SCS）虽设为默认值5，但在不同数据集上可能需要进一步调优以获得最佳性能。"
    ],
